Q3 ‚Äì Sync vs Async
Your answer: ‚ö†Ô∏è Small correction needed
Synchronous ‚â† stateful necessarily.
Correct version:
Synchronous service waits for an immediate response, while asynchronous service does not block and receives the response later via callback or separate flow.
‚úîÔ∏è Key distinction = blocking vs non-blocking, not stateful
